          "description": "There are some very kind and empathetic Doctors working here, but the inner workings of this establishment is truly sad. I came into this office to see if I have a diagnosis for fibromyalgia. I understand that multiple test have to be taken to rule out if it could possibly be another medical issue. However, the first Doctor I had an appointment with in August and was discussing my symptoms with, and I thought would be the main medical professional I would be communicating with moving forward in this process of gaining a diagnosis or not. I have never spoken with again, or had a followup. Since the ending of August I have had literally 22 appointments seen multiple Doctors and still no answer to what I first came in this clinic for. As other reviewers have mentioned this place will run your insurance up! So please make sure you know what is the reason for certain test being ordered. As well, certain medical assistant's within this company need to be educated on how to communicate with clients in a respectful and professional level. Being yelled at and having the phone hung up on me this past weekend, did it for me. After I read other reviews stating this establishment's incompetency and how they treat their clients. That is all I needed to know! Take your chances here if you want to.",
